text: Ko Korsten (2 May 1895 - 3 October 1981) was a Dutch swimmer. He competed in the men's 100 metre freestyle event at the 1920 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1895 births Category:1981 deaths Category:Dutch male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of the Netherlands Category:Swimmers at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:Swimmers from Amsterdam Category:Male freestyle swimmers
